ok for those of you having my prob, i finally solved it (and feeling pretty stoopid) -->

the 'computer id' is a number of alphanumerics generated within the macdrive activation window, not anything to do with the computer name permanently linked to your computer. it's just a long string of digits. When you put the generated serial into the first box of the activation window, a computer id appears below it. you take this and put it back into the second window of the keygen.
